    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a full kettle</p><p>Add your<strong> pine kernel & seed mix</strong> to a large pan over a medium heat and cook for 2-3 min, stirring occasionally, until nicely toasted</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p><p>Once done, transfer the <strong>toasted seeds</strong> to a<strong> food processor</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
