    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pine kernels & seeds are toasting, chop your<strong> tomato[es]</strong> into wedges and add them to a baking tray with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20 min or until softened – these are your <strong>roasted tomatoes</strong></p>",
