      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>farfalle</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the farfalle for an initial 9 min</p><p>Grate your <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong></p>",
