    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel your<strong> garlic </strong>and add it to the <strong>food processor</strong> with your<strong> basil </strong>(chuck it in, stalks and all!),<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>,<strong> </strong>2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span>[4 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong>, your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>soft cheese </strong>and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong></p><p>Blitz until well combined and smooth – this is your <strong>extra</strong> <strong>creamy pesto</strong></p>",
