    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, drain the <strong>farfalle &</strong> <strong>green beans</strong>, then return them to the pot with the <strong>creamy pesto</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until fully coated – this is your <strong>extra</strong> <strong>creamy pesto pasta</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
